				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n/B%E1%BA%A1c-m%E1%BB%87nh-o%C3%A1n/poem-8GS_o143UmqNkzGwSkKurQ">Bạc mệnh oán - 薄命怨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n/author-Ry0GXj_uifS6AejvZUIukQ">Thanh Tâm tài nhân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%90oan-Th%E1%BB%A5c/B%E1%BB%87nh-trung-h%E1%BB%89-t%C3%A2n-nguy%E1%BB%87t/poem-5LCgKX6CD-kW-rjrdzZk5A">Bệnh trung hỉ tân nguyệt - 病中喜新月</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%90oan-Th%E1%BB%A5c/author-6PN_wShlbQzgayvDwZcw5A">Vương Đoan Thục</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-V%C4%83n-Ngh%E1%BB%8B-I/C%E1%BA%A3m-t%C3%A1c/poem-szJiFMue4vqdBWAN1YOc0A">Cảm tác - 感作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-V%C4%83n-Ngh%E1%BB%8B-I/author-j2yv60iLSGVWsUs_D51NxQ">Phạm Văn Nghị (I)</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/%C4%90%C3%B4ng-th%C3%A0nh-cao-th%E1%BA%A3-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/poem-6XVwPhUIJqi9zmyHGgTB6g">Đông thành cao thả trường - 東城高且長</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-K%E1%BB%B3-Di/Ho%E1%BA%A1-th%C3%A1i-t%E1%BB%AD-th%E1%BA%BF-t%E1%BB%AD-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-t2jMuF0IG4VFqYCFs80c0w">Hoạ thái tử thế tử vận - 和太子世子韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-K%E1%BB%B3-Di/author-68k6cojsSnekI8p1Pt6xDg">Triệu Kỳ Di</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Th%C3%BAc-Tr%E1%BB%B1c/Nguy%C3%AAn-nh%E1%BA%ADt-t%E1%BB%A9-ti%E1%BB%83u-nhi-ti%E1%BB%81n-t%E1%BB%A5c-c%E1%BB%AD-h%C6%B0-s%E1%BB%95-t%C3%A1c/poem-rpq-sUQrIv1oh4u-ZxezJQ">Nguyên nhật tứ tiểu nhi tiền tục cử hư sổ tác - 元日賜小兒錢俗舉虛數作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Th%C3%BAc-Tr%E1%BB%B1c/author-0CTnEDQGEKViETWZXrhgww">Phan Thúc Trực</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Quy%E1%BB%83n-nh%C4%A9-1/poem-FDn1yWV2KHlH0K7Ksr9QNw">Quyển nhĩ 1 - 卷耳 1</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Thi%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%A5n/poem-xfUL0RFU1M6WV9XOi__Sxg">Thiên vấn - 天問</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1nh-Giao/Thu-ho%C3%A0i-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-QuT2H1faZndrv4CV2Ix5uQ">Thu hoài kỳ 2 - 秋懷其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1nh-Giao/author-lb0C1LYxo0fcanV11dmAog">Mạnh Giao</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/T%E1%BB%A9-m%E1%BA%ABu-1/poem-_9dglZaWwuilpaUxxrnXAQ">Tứ mẫu 1 - 四牡 1</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br></div>	</div>
